5. Tradeoffs and open questions you want me to decide before any code lands.

**Don't:**
- Treat DeepSeek's FP8 / `weight_scale_inv` convention as universal — other
  quantization schemes (per-row scales, per-tensor scales, different suffixes)
  exist and a future model may use them.
- Hoist per-model rename logic into a shared module; renames are inherently
  per-model.
- Propose backwards-compat shims; update callers directly.

